umarin deriv. that was produced is an appropriate precursor for the synthesis of \u03b3-rubromycin, purpuromycin, and heliquinomycin.", " >> More from SciFinder ", "\u00ae", "https://chemport.cas.org/services/resolver?origin=ACS&resolution=options&coi=1%3ACAS%3A528%3ADC%252BD3MXjtlSksL0%253D&md5=4153e2e25d29c87e28ef78071db27a22"], "figures": ["<img alt=\"figure\" src=\"/appl/literatum/publisher/achs/journals/content/jacsat/2012/jacsat.2012.134.issue-22/ja302991b/production/images/small/ja-2012-02991b_0014.gif\">", "<img alt=\"figure\" src=\"/appl/literatum/publisher/achs/journals/content/jacsat/2012/jacsat.2012.134.issue-22/ja302991b/production/images/small/ja-2012-02991b_0015.gif\">", "<img alt=\"figure\" src=\"/appl/literatum/publisher/achs/journals/content/jacsat/2012/jacsat.2012.134.issue-22/ja302991b/production/images/small/ja-2012-02991b_0008.gif\">", "<img alt=\"figure\" src=\"/appl/literatum/publisher/achs/journals/content/jacsat/2012/jacsat.2012.134.issue-22/ja302991b/production/images/small/ja-2012-02991b_0001.gif\">", "<img alt=\"figure\" src=\"/appl/literatum/publisher/achs/journals/content/jacsat/2012/jacsat.2012.134.issue-22/ja302991b/production/images/small/ja-2012-02991b_0002.gif\">", "<img alt=\"figure\" src=\"/appl/literatum/publisher/achs/journals/content/jacsat/2012/jacsat.2012.134.issue-22/ja302991b/production/images/small/ja-2012-02991b_0003.gif\">", "<img alt=\"figure\" src=\"/appl/literatum/publisher/achs/journals/content/jacsat/2012/jacsat.2012.134.issue-22/ja302991b/production/images/small/ja-2012-02991b_0004.gif\">", "<img alt=\"figure\" src=\"/appl/literatum/publisher/achs/journals/content/jacsat/2012/jacsat.2012.134.issue-22/ja302991b/production/images/small/ja-2012-02991b_0005.gif\">", "<img alt=\"figure\" src=\"/appl/literatum/publisher/achs/journals/content/jacsat/2012/jacsat.2012.134.issue-22/ja302991b/production/images/small/ja-2012-02991b_0006.gif\">", "<img alt=\"figure\" src=\"/appl/literatum/publisher/achs/journals/content/jacsa